221114.name: New Equipment Development Plan I
221114.memo:
✘Consumes the items and resources.
➣Rewards:
¶First choice: Either a New Model Artillery Armament Materials OR a New Model Aviation Armament Materials OR five Development Materials
¶Second choice: Either a New Model Armament Materials OR a New Model Rocket Development Materials OR three Screws
221114.detail: Have three 35.6cm Twin Gun Mounts, 8 Flamethrowers and 800 Bauxite. Scrap 3 Small Cal. Main Guns, 3 Medium Cal. Main Guns and 3 Secondary Guns.

240363.name: [10th Anniversary Quest] Mutsuki-class Destroyers, Exercises!
240363.memo:
➣Rewards:
¶First choice: Either a Skilled Lookouts OR four 25mm Single Autocannon Mounts OR a Reinforcement Expansion
¶Second choice: Either a ★3 12cm Single Gun Mount Kai 2 OR a ★3 61cm Triple (Oxygen) Torpedo Mount)
240363.detail: Secure 5 A-Rank+ victories in Exercises within the same day using 4 Mutsuki-class DD and up to 2 additional ships.

240448.name: [10th Anniversary Quest] 10th Anniversary Logistics Expedition
240448.memo:
➣Rewards:
¶First choice: Either 8800 Fuel OR eight Screws
¶Second choice: Either ten Development Materials OR two Daihatsu Landing Craft OR 3900 Bauxite
240448.detail: Complete Expeditions 5, A1, 9 and 11 once each, and Expedition 7 three times.

240971.name: [Limited] 9th Anniversary Fleet, Set Sail!
240971.memo:
➣Rewards:
¶First choice: Either nine Development Materials OR nine Buckets
¶Second choice: Either three Type 99 Dive Bomber Model 22 OR a Type 99 Dive Bomber Model 22 (Skilled) OR a Reinforcement Expansion
240971.detail: Sortie a CL as flagship, 2 DD and up to 3 additional ships to [W1-1], [W1-2], [W1-3], [W1-4] and [W1-5]. S-Rank each boss node.

240972.name: [Limited] 9th Anniversary Fleet, Extra Operation!
240972.memo: ➣Rewards either six New Model Aviation Armament Materials OR 3 Medals OR a 51cm Twin Gun Mount
240972.detail: Sortie a CVL as flagship, 2 DD and up to 3 additional ships to [W2-3], [W3-5], [W7-4] and [W6-4]. S-Rank each boss node.

240979.name: [Limited-Time Mission] Maritime Escort for Resource Recovery
240979.memo:
➣Rewards:
¶First choice: Either eight Buckets OR 4000 Steel OR 10 Development Materials
¶Second choice: Either a Medal OR 8000 Fuel OR a Furniture Fairy
240979.detail: Sortie to [W1-2], [W1-3], [W1-5], [W1-6-N] and [W2-3]. S-Rank all relevant boss nodes.
